290
00:20:00.155 --> 00:20:02.375
Luca. I know. okay. baby?

291
00:20:02.418 --> 00:20:05.943
But it's time to go now. okay?

292
00:20:07.858 --> 00:20:09.338
Okay.

293
00:20:09.382 --> 00:20:10.905
That's my good boy.

294
00:20:10.948 --> 00:20:12.733
